Package: pulldb
Version: 0.0.10
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: PestRoutes Engineering <engineering@pestroutes.com>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.12), python3-venv, systemd, adduser, bash
Homepage: https://github.com/CharlesHandshy/pullDB
Description: pullDB database restore tooling
 pullDB retrieves production backups and restores them into development
 environments. This package installs the system scaffolding, service
 templates, and installer used to configure the worker daemon.
